\(lqpseudo\-SQL\(rq
statements, run
\fBmysqlbinlog\fR
with the
\fB\-\-verbose\fR
or
\fB\-v\fR
option\&. This output level also shows table partition information where applicable\&. The output contains lines beginning with
###:
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
